---
title: Beef Shepherd's Pie with Garlic Mash & Rocket Salad
description: Nothing beats a comforting shepherd’s pie on a cold winter's night. Whether it’s the cheesy mashed potato on top or the rich
beef and veggie filling, it’ll warm you up from the inside out and bring back those fond memories of home-cooked favourites.
